<HEADLINE> Chile's Foreign Debt Reaches 35.049 Bln U.S. Dls </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SANTIAGO, August 7 (Xinhua) -- Chile's foreign debt reached 35.
049 billion U.S. dollars to June 30 this year, including 5.727
billion dollars of public debt and 29.322 billion dollars of
private one, according to a report delivered by the Central Bank
on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The document specifies that the medium and long-term foreign
debt to-date reaches 30.282 billion dollars, with public sector's
4.703 billion dollars and private sector's 25.579 billion dollars.
</P>
</TEXT>
