400ER arrived at the Beijing Capital International Airport today
and carried out flight demonstrations.
</P>
<P>
The fuselage of twin-aisle 767-400ER is about 201 feet (61
meters), 21 feet (six meters) longer than the 767-300ER. It can
accommodate 245 to 375 passengers with a maximum a fly a distance
of 10,460 kilometers.
