<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, August 7 (Xinhua) -- The Sensitive Index (Sensex)
rose on the Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE) Monday as the software
major, Infosys Tech, took the center stage on Local Funds buying.
</P>
