<HEADLINE> HK Stocks Close Up 1.73 Percent </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 7 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks closed up 301.
55 points, or 1.73 percent, at 17,727.25 Monday, led by bank and
property shares.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 12.231 billion HK dollars (1.568 billion U.S.
dollars), slightly up from the previous day's 12.162 billion HK
dollars (1.559 billion U.S. dollars).
</P>
