Enterprises Index up 1.82 percent and Hang Seng China-Affiliated
Corp Index 1.01 percent.
</P>
<P>
Hang Seng IT Index and Hang Seng IT Portfolio Index increased 1.
33 percent and 0.73 percent.
</P>
<P>
The Hang Seng index soared 113.11 points, or 0.65 percent, to
open at 17,538.81 Monday. The stock prices continued to rise and
closed the morning session at 17,631.02. 
