<HEADLINE> Shanghai B-share Market Jump at Monday Close </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 7 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai B-share market index
shot up 3.33 points, or 5.17 percent, to the intraday high of 67.
63 at the close on Monday.
</P>
<P>
Turnover was 38.31 million U.S. dollars, which was 7.82 million
U.S. dollars or 25.65 percent more than the total of last Friday,
according to Homeway, China's leading on-line financial and
securities advisory company.
</P>
